videos.headline: LSU's Divinity JR. picks off Fitzgerald
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald throws a pass up the middle which is intercepted by Michael Divinity Jr.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald sacked on fourth down
videos.description: Mississippi State QB goes for it on fourth down, but ends up getting sacked by Grant Delpit as the Bulldogs turn it over on downs.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald picked off for the third time
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald's pass gets intercepted by LSU's John Battle, Fitzgerald's third INT of the game.

videos.headline: Orgeron says LSU is going to enjoy this win
videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron breaks down his team's win over Mississippi State on Saturday night.

videos.headline: LSU's D carries them past Mississippi State
videos.description: LSU's defense forces Nick Fitzgerald into four interceptions and the Tigers take down the Bulldogs 19-3.
